    <div class="katanna wf-section">
      <div class="text-block-2 title bear">KATANA CASE STUDY</div>
      <div class="div-block-13"><a href="#bear" class="tab bear-tab w-inline-block"></a><a href="#KATANNA" class="tab w-inline-block w--current"></a><a href="#frog" class="tab frog w-inline-block"></a></div>
      <div class="text-block-2">This bear was commissioned to us by an indie game. The client wanted a massive armored bear. Here is how the concept art progressed over the course of a week. The client was extremely responsive and had clear feedback.														</div>

      <img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb144c0588b1e707_katana%204%20copy.png" loading="lazy" width="1228" srcset="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb144c0588b1e707_katana%204%20copy-p-500.png 500w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb144c0588b1e707_katana%204%20copy-p-800.png 800w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb144c0588b1e707_katana%204%20copy-p-1080.png 1080w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb144c0588b1e707_katana%204%20copy-p-1600.png 1600w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb144c0588b1e707_katana%204%20copy.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, (max-width: 1439px) 75vw, (max-width: 1919px) 699.9884643554688px, 1199.988525390625px" alt="">
      <div class="div-block-13"><a href="#bear" class="tab bear-tab w-inline-block"></a><a href="#KATANNA" class="tab w-inline-block w--current"></a><a href="#frog" class="tab frog w-inline-block"></a></div>

      <div class="text-block-2">This set of katanas was commissioned to us by a P2E game. &nbsp;The client wanted four different rarities/classes of the same weapon. &nbsp;This job took one week of communication between our team and the clients to iron out the concept and form. &nbsp;Then another week of production. &nbsp;They had no corrections and accepted the finished product as-is. &nbsp;Their total cost was $1,800usd. &nbsp;They received: stl (ready to 3D print file), glb (3D viewer file), fbx (game-ready mesh/rig import file), and textures (colors and patterns for game engines).</div>
      <img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f5718657a152a301dec1_katana%201%20copy.png" loading="lazy" width="2151" srcset="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f5718657a152a301dec1_katana%201%20copy-p-500.png 500w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f5718657a152a301dec1_katana%201%20copy-p-800.png 800w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f5718657a152a301dec1_katana%201%20copy-p-1080.png 1080w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f5718657a152a301dec1_katana%201%20copy-p-1600.png 1600w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f5718657a152a301dec1_katana%201%20copy.png 1666w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 83vw, (max-width: 1439px) 75vw, 60vw" alt="" class="image-11">
      <img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571e4619fe6526575f5_katana%202%20copy.png" loading="lazy" width="1871" alt="" class="image-10">
      <img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571de9f4a535c8de61c_katana%20%20copy.png" loading="lazy" srcset="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571de9f4a535c8de61c_katana%20%20copy-p-500.png 500w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571de9f4a535c8de61c_katana%20%20copy-p-800.png 800w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571de9f4a535c8de61c_katana%20%20copy-p-1080.png 1080w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571de9f4a535c8de61c_katana%20%20copy-p-1600.png 1600w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571de9f4a535c8de61c_katana%20%20copy.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 83vw, (max-width: 1439px) 75vw, 60vw" alt="" class="image-4">
      <img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273fbecd84b9db051924346_reflect%201.png" loading="lazy" srcset="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273fbecd84b9db051924346_reflect%201-p-500.png 500w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273fbecd84b9db051924346_reflect%201-p-800.png 800w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273fbecd84b9db051924346_reflect%201-p-1080.png 1080w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273fbecd84b9db051924346_reflect%201-p-1600.png 1600w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273fbecd84b9db051924346_reflect%201.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 83vw, (max-width: 1439px) 75vw, 60vw" alt="" class="image-8">
      <img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb7631abbe90537d_kaaratana%20copy.png" loading="lazy" srcset="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb7631abbe90537d_kaaratana%20copy-p-500.png 500w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb7631abbe90537d_kaaratana%20copy-p-800.png 800w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb7631abbe90537d_kaaratana%20copy-p-1080.png 1080w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb7631abbe90537d_kaaratana%20copy-p-1600.png 1600w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6262efd7043c83bbf5b66ecd/6273f571bb7631abbe90537d_kaaratana%20copy.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 83vw, (max-width: 1439px) 75vw, 60vw" alt="" class="image-5">

      <div class="text-block-2">Here's what they had to say: "UA gave us EXACTLY what we needed. &nbsp;Their team spent a ton of time making sure everything was how we liked it. &nbsp;We got WIPs along the way everyday and they were patient. &nbsp;They even thought of things we didn't to make sure the 3D prints were "water-tight". &nbsp;Highly recommend. &nbsp;-(NDA), team.</div>

